The '''''Caelus''''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Cruiser/Legends|cruiser]] stationed at [[Durren]] in the [[Meridian sector/Legends|Meridian sector]] in [[9 ABY/Legends|9 ABY]]. It was one of two New Republic warships dispatched to deal with [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] attacks on nearby [[Ampliquen]].

